            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Dis Manibus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berius</ex></expan> Claudius Artemidori <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Quir</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Phoebus Tiberio<lb break="no" n="4"/>politanus vivos <note>sic</note> sibi <lb n="5"/>et Piliae Fidae Vasiensi <lb n="6"/>uxori carissimae
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription was found in an unknown place in Tarentaise area. (B): CIL 12 05718: Z. 5 Filiae Fidae. Material: unbestimmt, vielleicht Stein.</p>
            </div>
